ient absorption called enterocytes also express the RNAs for two proteins, which makes them vulnerable to the coronavirus."SOURCES: Nature, Cell.comhttps://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-0868-6https://www.cell.com/pb-assets/products/coronavirus/CELL_CELL-D-20-00767.pdf***For story suggestions please contact tips@nextanimation.com.twFor technical and editorial support, please contact:Asia: +61 2 93 73 1841Europe: +44 20 7542 7599Americas and Latam: +1 800 738 8377]]></description>
